features for next releases

	
	Planned
		- Character support; (http://stackoverflow.com/questions/405684/php-mysql-with-encoding-problems)
		- selectable fields (mac, switch, port, ...)
		- subnet splitting;
		- search for available subnets;
		- translations (XML);
		- Sorting of IP addresses;
		- Sorting of subnets;
		- SMTP auth;
		- request from subnets for non-privileged accounts;
				
	bugs
